ji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bde0af84608210493cf7013e0af8af4fae7333e0","tid":2258672,"uid":342200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T03:49:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前就係放權俾警察，造成今日既局面。<br />\n今日又提議放權俾醫生，只會不斷有更多特權階級出現。<br />\n<br />\n要一個人以道德標準去制衡自己擁有既過大權力係有可能，但當一個團隊一個部門一個機構，越來越多人擁有特別權力，後果很慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"8e6f90d70ccd28eabf5ae057666e3ed97cb6da26","tid":2258672,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T08:25:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc57b27b94452c27d856be9ce38f02d62809481e","tid":2258672,"uid":138790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T08:26:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}